text: Tahir Bizenjo is a Pakistani politician who has been a Member of the Senate of Pakistan, since March 2018. ==Political career== Bizenjo was elected to the Senate of Pakistan as a candidate of National Party on technocrat seat from Balochistan in 2018 Pakistani Senate election. He took oath as Senator on 12 March 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Senate of Pakistan Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Tahir Bizenjo
